info.name: Black and White - Roblox
info.description: This is the fixed version of the original, now the background works. Credits go to >Uselesshunger - the creator of the artwork<, also the gif is actually meant to be film damage and credits to >unworse< for the colour choices. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
info.additionalInfo: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Won't work for tablets/iPads or phones. The style not appearing/downloading bug is an issue with the extension, not style.
